Teke - Hunkutu Chief\n* Mbaye Dieng - Songa\n* Lorraine Kadye - Zouya\n* Martin Strecker - Professor \n* Furkan Bayraktar - Fazil\n* Mustafa Dok - Tefo\n\n== Production ==\n=== Filming ===\nPrincipal photography for the movie began on 3 September 2018.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.posta.com.tr/sahan-gokbakar-recep-ivedik-6nin-ilk-cekim-goruntusunu-paylasti-2044372 |title=\u015eahan G\u00f6kbakar, Recep \u0130vedik 6'n\u0131n ilk \u00e7ekim g\u00f6r\u00fcnt\u00fcs\u00fcn\u00fc payla\u015ft\u0131 |work=Posta |date=3 September 2018 |accessdate=6 September 2018}}</ref> It was announced that part of the shootings would take place in the longoz forest in [[Karacabey]] district of [[Bursa Province|Bursa]].<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aa.com.tr/tr/kultur-sanat/recep-ivedik-6-karacabey-longozunda-cekilecek/1215631 |title='Recep \u0130vedik 6' Karacabey Longozu'nda \u00e7ekilecek |agency=Anadolu Agency |first=Ayhan |last=Fidan |location=Bursa |date=27 July 2018 |accessdate=28 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{IMDb title|7399138|Recep \u0130vedik 6}}\n\n{{Togan and \u015eahan G\u00f6kbakar}}\n\n[[Category:2019 films]]\n[[Category:2010s comedy films]]\n[[Category:Turkish comedy films]]\n[[Category:Turkish-language films]]\n[[Category:Turkish sequel films]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Films set in Kenya]]\n", "text_old": "{{infobox film\n| name              = Recep \u0130vedik 6\n| image             = Recep \u0130vedik 6.jpg\n| caption           = Theatrical release poster\n| director          = [[Togan G\u00f6kbakar]]\n| producer          = [[\u015eahan G\u00f6kbakar]]<br>Togan G\u00f6kbakar\n| writer            = Togan G\u00f6kbakar<br>\u015eahan G\u00f6kbakar\n| starring          = \u015eahan G\u00f6kbakar<br>[[Nurullah \u00c7elebi]]\n| music             = \u00d6mer \u00d6zg\u00fcr<br>Jingle Jungle\n| cinematography    = Gerard Simon\n| editing           = Ersin Eker\n| production_companies= [[\u00c7ama\