eral zones. For the first time a separate league for [[farm team]]s was set up.\n\n==A Lyga==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n\n|team1=FBK|name_FBK=[[FBK Kaunas]]\n|team2=S\u016aD|name_S\u016aD=[[FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117|S\u016bduva]]\n|team3=EKR|name_EKR=[[FK Ekranas|Ekranas]]\n|team4=\u017dAL|name_\u017dAL=[[FK \u017dalgiris Vilnius|\u017dalgiris]]\n|team5=V\u0116T|name_V\u0116T=[[FK V\u0117tra|V\u0117tra]]\n|team6=ATL|name_ATL=[[FK Atlantas|Atlantas]]\n|team7=VIL|name_VIL=[[FC Vilnius|Vilnius]]\n|team8=\u0160IA|name_\u0160IA=[[FK \u0160iauliai|\u0160iauliai]]\n|team9=\u0160IL|name_\u0160IL=[[FK \u0160ilut\u0117|\u0160ilut\u0117]]\n|team10=IAE|name_IAE=[[Interas-AE Visaginas]]\n|win_FBK=25|draw_FBK=8|loss_FBK=3|gf_FBK=91|ga_FBK=26|status_FBK=C\n|win_S\u016aD=20|draw_S\u016aD=8|loss_S\u016aD=8|gf_S\u016aD=66|ga_S\u016aD=34\n|win_EKR=19|draw_EKR=9|loss_EKR=8|gf_EKR=83|ga_EKR=36\n|win_\u017dAL=18|draw_\u017dAL=10|loss_\u017dAL=8|gf_\u017dAL=64|ga_\u017dAL=34\n|win_V\u0116T=18|draw_V\u0116T=7|loss_V\u0116T=11|gf_V\u0116T=55|ga_V\u0116T=30\n|win_ATL=13|draw_ATL=6|loss_ATL=17|gf_ATL=54|ga_ATL=45\n|win_VIL=13|draw_VIL=6|loss_VIL=17|gf_VIL=54|ga_VIL=63|status_VIL=R\n|win_\u0160IA=13|draw_\u0160IA=6|loss_\u0160IA=17|gf_\u0160IA=47|ga_\u0160IA=50\n|win_\u0160IL=6|draw_\u0160IL=4|loss_\u0160IL=26|gf_\u0160IL=28|ga_\u0160IL=86\n|win_IAE=2|draw_IAE=2|loss_IAE=32|gf_IAE=16|ga_IAE=154|status_IAE=R\n|col_CL1=green1|text_CL1=Qualification to [[2008\u201309 UEFA Champions League#First qualifying round|Champions League first qualifying round]]\n|result1=CL1\n|col_UC1=blue1|text_UC1=Qualification to [[2008\u201309 UEFA Cup#First qualifying round|UEFA Cup first qualifying round]]\n|result2=UC1|result5=UC1\n|col_IC1=#ccccff|text_IC1=Qualification to [[2008 UEFA Intertoto Cup#First round|Intertoto Cup first round]]\n|result3=IC1\n|col_R1=red1|text_R1=Relegation to [[I Lyga]]\n|result7=R1\n|col_R2=black1|text_R2=Defunct after end of season\n|result10=R2